om\": 9833, \"to\": 9841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m better.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri Richardson: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m not back I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m better\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dpic.twitter.com/2iNR9VVeOP \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Travis Miller (@travismillerx13)July 8, 2023 Richardson elaborated on the saying in aninterview with Voguepublished last month.\", \"from\": 9852, \"to\": 10089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9882, \"end\": 9892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.733131325292241e-33, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"better\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009dpic.twitter.com/2iNR9VVeOP \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 Travis Miller\", \"from\": 9917, \"to\": 9970}, {\"ngram\": \"@travismillerx13)July\", \"from\": 9972, \"to\": 9993}, {\"ngram\": \"Richardson\", \"from\": 10002, \"to\": 10012}, {\"ngram\": \"the saying\", \"from\": 10027, \"to\": 10037}, {\"ngram\": \"aninterview\", \"from\": 10041, \"to\": 10052}, {\"ngram\": \"Voguepublished\", \"from\": 10058, \"to\": 10072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t just mean I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m a better runner,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 10090, \"to\": 10148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 10113, \"to\": 10118}, {\"ngram\": \"a better runner\", \"from\": 10119, \"to\": 10134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s beyond that.\", \"from\": 10149, \"to\": 10171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10149, \"to\": 10158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m better at being Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri.\", \"from\": 10172, \"to\": 10206, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 10172, \"to\": 10177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m better at being myself.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s easy to perceive Olympians as athletes.\", \"from\": 10207, \"to\": 10287, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m\", \"from\": 10207, \"to\": 10212}, {\"ngram\": \"myself.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 10229, \"to\": 10246}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 10264, \"to\": 10273}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 10277, \"to\": 10285}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what they are, it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s what they do, and boy do they do it well.\", \"from\": 10288, \"to\": 10358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But lest we forget that the whole is greater than the sum of its parts, or that the parts extend far beyond the confines of athleticism alone.\", \"from\": 10359, \"to\": 10501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the whole\", \"from\": 10383, \"to\": 10392}, {\"ngram\": \"the sum\", \"from\": 10409, \"to\": 10416}, {\"ngram\": \"its parts\", \"from\": 10420, \"to\": 10429}, {\"ngram\": \"the parts\", \"from\": 10439, \"to\": 10448}, {\"ngram\": \"the confines\", \"from\": 10467, \"to\": 10479}, {\"ngram\": \"athleticism\", \"from\": 10483, \"to\": 10494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These redemption narratives speak to their achievements, but they also function to challenge (if not altogether reframe) the notion of what it means to be a great athlete \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 before they were Olympians, they were Simone, Sunisa and Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri.\\u00c2 This knowledge also allows us laypeople to find some comfort in compelling Olympic comeback tales.\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10847, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These redemption narratives\", \"from\": 10502, \"to\": 10529}, {\"ngram\": \"their achievements\", \"from\": 10539, \"to\": 10557}, {\"ngram\": \"the notion\", \"from\": 10623, \"to\": 10633}, {\"ngram\": \"a great athlete\", \"from\": 10657, \"to\": 10672}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 10694, \"to\": 10703}, {\"ngram\": \"Simone\", \"from\": 10715, \"to\": 10721}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunisa\", \"from\": 10723, \"to\": 10729}, {\"ngram\": \"Sha\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099Carri\", \"from\": 10734, \"to\": 10745}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 10746, \"to\": 10747}, {\"ngram\": \"This knowledge\", \"from\": 10748, \"to\": 10762}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10775, \"to\": 10777}, {\"ngram\": \"some comfort\", \"from\": 10796, \"to\": 10808}, {\"ngram\": \"compelling Olympic comeback tales\", \"from\": 10812, \"to\": 10845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the most honest yet hard-to-grapple-with truth about Olympians is that they\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re quite like us \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 their inspiring stories serve as reminders of our own capabilities (albeit less coordinated ones), goading us to take the rarely invested time to reflect inward on what we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve accomplished in our own lives.\", \"from\": 10848, \"to\": 11162, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most honest yet hard-to-grapple-with truth\", \"from\": 10856, \"to\": 10902}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 10909, \"to\": 10918}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 10948, \"to\": 10950}, {\"ngram\": \"their inspiring stories\", \"from\": 10955, \"to\": 10978}, {\"ngram\": \"reminders\", \"from\": 10988, \"to\": 10997}, {\"ngram\": \"our own capabilities\", \"from\": 11001, \"to\": 11021}, {\"ngram\": \"less coordinated ones\", \"from\": 11030, \"to\": 11051}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 11062, \"to\": 11064}, {\"ngram\": \"the rarely invested time\", \"from\": 11073, \"to\": 11097}, {\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099ve\", \"from\": 11124, \"to\": 11131}, {\"ngram\": \"our own lives\", \"from\": 11148, \"to\": 11161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps, they might even encourage us to hold our hearts and minds in kinder regard, refuting society\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s prevailing disregard for mental health.\\u00c2 After winning the 100-meter dash final at the Stade de France, U.S. sprinterNoah Lylespublished a candidtweet:\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI have Asthma, allergies, dyslexia, ADD, anxiety, and Depression.\", \"from\": 11163, \"to\": 11489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 11357, \"end\": 11372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 11431, \"end\": 11437, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Asthma\", \"types\": [\"Q12136\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asthma\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 11198, \"to\": 11200}, {\"ngram\": \"our hearts\", \"from\": 11209, \"to\": 11219}, {\"ngram\": \"minds\", \"from\": 11224, \"to\": 11229}, {\"ngram\": \"kinder regard\", \"from\": 11233, \"to\": 11246}, {\"ngram\": \"prevailing disregard\", \"from\": 11269, \"to\": 11289}, {\"ngram\": \"mental health\", \"from\": 11294, \"to\": 11307}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. sprinterNoah\", \"from\": 11373, \"to\": 11390}, {\"ngram\": \"a candidtweet\", \"from\": 11406, \"to\": 11419}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 11420, \"to\": 11424}, {\"ngram\": \"allergies\", \"from\": 11438, \"to\": 11447}, {\"ngram\": \"dyslexia\", \"from\": 11449, \"to\": 11457}, {\"ngram\": \"ADD\", \"from\": 11459, \"to\": 11462}, {\"ngram\": \"anxiety\", \"from\": 11464, \"to\": 11471}, {\"ngram\": \"Depression\", \"from\": 11477, \"to\": 11487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I will tell you that what you have does not define what you can become.\", \"from\": 11490, \"to\": 11565, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Why Not You!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Lyles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 message quite cloudlessly encapsulates the crux of the multifaceted elements of an athlete, of a human being \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 to become theworld\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fastest man,he had to nurtureallof his needs, not simply fine-tune his physicality.\\u00c2 His remarks are also a steady reminder of the way disability, despite being an ostensible impediment, can be worked with while being exceptionally athletic.\", \"from\": 11566, \"to\": 11971, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Not You!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Lyles\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 message\", \"from\": 11570, \"to\": 11599}, {\"ngram\": \"the crux\", \"from\": 11631, \"to\": 11639}, {\"ngram\": \"the multifaceted elements\", \"from\": 11643, \"to\": 11668}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 11672, \"to\": 11682}, {\"ngram\": \"a human being\", \"from\": 11687, \"to\": 11700}, {\"ngram\": \"theworld\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s fastest man\", \"from\": 11715, \"to\": 11739}, {\"ngram\": \"his needs\", \"from\": 11763, \"to\": 11772}, {\"ngram\": \"fine-tune his physicality\", \"from\": 11785, \"to\": 11810}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 11811, \"to\": 11812}, {\"ngram\": \"His remarks\", \"from\": 11813, \"to\": 11824}, {\"ngram\": \"a steady reminder\", \"from\": 11834, \"to\": 11851}, {\"ngram\": \"the way disability\", \"from\": 11855, \"to\": 11873}, {\"ngram\": \"an ostensible impediment\", \"from\": 11889, \"to\": 11913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Olympics end this Sunday, the Paralympics will follow, commencing in Paris on Aug. 28.\", \"from\": 11972, \"to\": 12067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12050, \"end\": 12055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.9680431784347923e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Par